title: Airhead Blast 2014 HD
description: You'll have a real blast on Airhead Blast! The 4 neoprene knuckle guards and deluxe nylon covered handles provide a sure and comfortable grip. The heavy-duty virgin PVC bladder has electronically welded seams and a Boston valve for quick inflating and deflating. Blast has a double stitched nylon cover, reinforced internal tow harness and a self-draining floor vent. You'll love the eye-catching graphics on this 1 rider 54˝ (deflated) round towable!
